webpage.label: web page URL
webpage.description: The URL of a web page about this item.

archivedWebpage.label: archived page URL
archivedWebpage.description: The URL of an archived web page about this item, which may no longer be available in the web.

wikipedia.label: wikipedia page URL
wikipedia.description: The URL of an (English) Wikipedia article about this item.

orcid.label: orcid
orcid.description: An Open Researcher and Contributor ID.

creatorName.label: full creator name
creatorName.description: The full name of the creator.

primaryCreatorName.label: primary full creator name
primaryCreatorName.description: The primary full name of the creator.

creatorNote.label: creator note
creatorNote.description: An additional note about the creator.

affiliation.label: affiliation
affiliation.description: A (past or present) affiliation of the creator. (Remark: This property currently just gives literal xsd:string values until institutions are modelled as proper entities.)

primaryAffiliation.label: primary affiliation
primaryAffiliation.description: The primary affiliation of the creator. (Remark: This property currently just gives literal xsd:string values until institutions are modelled as proper entities.)

awardWebpage.label: award page URL
awardWebpage.description: The URL of a web page about an award received by this creator.

homepage.label: homepage URL
homepage.description: The URL of an academic homepage of this creator.

primaryHomepage.label: primary homepage URL
primaryHomepage.description: The primary URL of an academic homepage of this creator.

authorOf.label: author of
authorOf.description: The creator is the author of the publication.

editorOf.label: editor of
editorOf.description: The creator is the editor of the publication.

possibleActualCreator.label: possible actual creator
possibleActualCreator.description: This ambiguous creator may be (or may be not) just a disambiguation proxy for the other creator. Further actual creator candidates are possible.

proxyAmbiguousCreator.label: proxy ambiguous creator
proxyAmbiguousCreator.description: This creator (and any of her fellow homonymous creators) is also represented by the given ambiguous creator in cases where the authorship of a publication is undetermined.

signatureCreator.label: signature creator
signatureCreator.description: A linked creator of the publication.

signatureDblpName.label: signature dblp name
signatureDblpName.description: A dblp name (including any possible trailing homonym number) that links the publication to a creator.

signatureOrcid.label: signature ORCID
signatureOrcid.description: An ORCID that links the publication to a creator.

signatureOrdinal.label: signature ordinal
signatureOrdinal.description: The ordinal number of this signature for the publication, starting with 1.

bibtexType.label: bibtex type
bibtexType.description: The bibtex type of the publication, e.g. book, inproceedings, etc.

createdBy.label: created by
createdBy.description: The publication is created by the creator.

authoredBy.label: authored by
authoredBy.description: The publication is authored by the creator.

editedBy.label: edited by
editedBy.description: The publication is edited by the creator.

numberOfCreators.label: number of creators
numberOfCreators.description: The number of creators who created this publication.

hasSignature.label: creator signature
hasSignature.description: A signature that links this publication to an creator.

documentPage.label: document page URL
documentPage.description: The URL of the electronic edition of the publication.

primarydocumentPage.label: primary document page URL
primarydocumentPage.description: The primary URL of the electronic edition of the publication.

listedOnTocPage.label: dblp ToC page url
listedOnTocPage.description: The url of the dblp table of contents page listing this publication.

publishedIn.label: published in
publishedIn.description: The name of the series, the journal, or the book in which the publication has been published. (Remark: This property currently just gives literal xsd:string values until journals and conference series are modelled as proper entities.)

publishedInSeries.label: published in series
publishedInSeries.description: The name of the series in which the publication has been published. (Remark: This is currently an intermediate property that will be removed once journals and conference series are modelled as proper entities.)

publishedInSeriesVolume.label: published in series volume
publishedInSeriesVolume.description: The volume of the series in which the publication has been published. (Remark: This is currently an intermediate property that will be removed once journals and conference series are modelled as proper entities.)

publishedInJournal.label: published in journal
publishedInJournal.description: The name of the journal in which the publication has been published. (Remark: This is currently an intermediate property that will be removed once journals and conference series are modelled as proper entities.)

publishedInJournalVolume.label: published in journal volume
publishedInJournalVolume.description: The volume of the journal in which the publication has been published. (Remark: This is currently an intermediate property that will be removed once journals and conference series are modelled as proper entities.)

publishedInJournalVolumeIssue.label: published in journal issue
publishedInJournalVolumeIssue.description: The issue of the journal in which the publication has been published. (Remark: This is currently an intermediate property that will be removed once journals and conference series are modelled as proper entities.)

publishedInBook.label: published in book
publishedInBook.description: The name of the book in which the publication has been published. (Remark: This is currently an intermediate property that will be removed once journals and conference series are modelled as proper entities.)

publishedInBookChapter.label: published in book chapter
publishedInBookChapter.description: The chapter of the book in which the publication has been published. (Remark: This is currently an intermediate property that will be removed once journals and conference series are modelled as proper entities.)

pagination.label: page numbers
pagination.description: The page numbers where the publication can be found.

yearOfEvent.label: year of event
yearOfEvent.description: The year the conference or workshop contribution has been presented.

yearOfPublication.label: year of publication
yearOfPublication.description: The year the publication's issue or volume has been published.

monthOfPublication.label: month of publication
monthOfPublication.description: The month the publication has been published.

publishedBy.label: publisher
publishedBy.description: The publisher of the publication. (Remark: This property currently just gives literal xsd:string values until publishers are modelled as proper entities.)

publishersAddress.label: publishers address
publishersAddress.description: The address of the publisher. (Remark: This is currently an intermediate property that will be removed once publishers are modelled as proper entities.)

thesisAcceptedBySchool.label: school
thesisAcceptedBySchool.description: The school where the publication (typically a thesis) has been accepted. (Remark: This property currently just gives literal xsd:string values until institutions are modelled as proper entities.)

publicationNote.label: publication note
publicationNote.description: An additional note to the publication.

Entity.label: Entity
Entity.description: A general, identifiable entity in dblp.

AmbiguousCreator.label: Ambiguous Creator
AmbiguousCreator.description: Not an actual creator, but an ambiguous proxy for an unknown number of unrelated actual creators. Associated publications do not have their true creators determined yet.

Person.label: Person
Person.description: An actual person, who is a creator of a publication.

Group.label: Group
Group.description: A creator alias used by a group or consortium of persons.

Signature.label: Signature
Signature.description: The information that links a publication to a creator.

AuthorSignature.label: Author Signature
AuthorSignature.description: The information that links a publication to an author.

EditorSignature.label: Editor Signature
EditorSignature.description: The information that links a publication to an editor.

Incollection.label: Incollection
Incollection.description: A part/chapter in a book or a collection.
